\c 16
\s Rwendo rwaPauro rwechipiri
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakasvika kuDhebhe neRistra; zvino tarira, ipapo paiva neumwe mudzidzi, wainzi Timotio, mwanakomana weumwe mukadzi muJudhakadzi waitenda, asi baba vake \add vaiva\add* muGiriki;
\v 2 waipupurirwa zvakanaka nehama dzepaRistra neIkoniyamu.
\v 3 Iye Pauro wakada kuti abude naye, ndokumutora aka\add mu\add*dzingisa nekuda kwevaJudha vaiva kunzvimbo idzo; nekuti vose vakange vachiziva baba vake, kuti muGiriki.
\v 4 Zvino vakati vachigura nemumaguta, vakavakumikidza zviga zvakatemwa nevaapositori nevakuru vaiva paJerusarema kuti vachengete.
\v 5 Naizvozvo kereke dzakasimbiswa parutendo, ndokuwedzera pauwandu zuva nezuva.
\p
\v 6 Zvino vakati vagura Frigia nedunhu reGaratia, vadziviswa neMweya Mutsvene kuparidza shoko paAsia,
\v 7 ndokuti vasvika pakatarisana neMisia vakaidza kuenda kuBhitinia; asi Mweya haana kuvatendera;
\v 8 zvino vakati vapfuura parutivi rweMisia vakaburukira kuTroasi.
\v 9 Chiratidzo ndokuonekwa kuna Pauro usiku; umwe murume muMakedhonia wakange amirepo, achimukumbira zvikuru achiti: Yambukira kuMakedhonia, utibatsire.
\v 10 Zvino wakati achiona chiratidzo, pakarepo tikatsvaka kubuda tiende kuMakedhonia, tapedza tichiti Ishe watidana kunoparidza evhangeri kwavari.
\s Pauro naSirasi paFiripi
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo takabva Troasi nechikepe, tikaruramira kuSamotirasi, fumewo kuNeapori,
\v 12 tikabvapowo, \add tikaenda\add* kuFiripi, rinova guta rekutanga redunhu reMakedhonia, raitongwa neimwe nyika; uye takagara mamwe mazuva muguta iro.
\v 13 Zvino nezuva resabata tikabuda kunze kweguta kurutivi rwerwizi, paifanira kuitirwa munyengetero; zvino takagara pasi tikataura nevakadzi vakange vaungana\add po\add*.
\v 14 Zvino umwe mukadzi wainzi Ridhiya, mukadzi mutengesi wezvine ruvara rwehute weguta reTiatira, wainamata Mwari, waka\add ti\add*nzwa; moyo wake Ishe waakazarura, kuti ateerere zvinhu zvinotaurwa naPauro.
\v 15 Zvino wakati abhabhatidzwa, neimba yake, akakumbira achiti: Kana maona kuti ndakatendeka kuna Ishe, pindai mumba mangu mugare. Zvino akatikumbirisa.
\p
\v 16 Zvino takati pataipinda kumunyengetero, umwe murandasikana waiva nemweya wekuuka wakasangana nesu, waivigira vatenzi vake mibairo mizhinji nekuuka.
\v 17 Iye wakatevera Pauro nesu, achidanidzira achiti: Vanhu ava varanda vaMwari Wekumusoro-soro, vanotiparidzira nzira yeruponeso.
\v 18 Zvino izvi wakazviita mazuva mazhinji. Pauro wakati asemburwa, akatendeuka, akati kumweya: Ndinokuraira muzita raJesu Kristu kuti ubude kwaari. Zvino ukabuda nenguva iyoyo.
\v 19 Vatenzi vake vakati vaona kuti tariro yemibairo yavo yaenda, vakabata Pauro naSirasi, vaka\add va\add*kakatira kudare pamberi pevatungamiriri,
\v 20 vakati vavauisa kuvatungamiriri vakati: Vanhu ava vanopesanisa guta redu, vari vaJudha,
\v 21 uye vanoparidza tsika dzisiri pamutemo kwatiri kugamuchira kana kuita, tiri vaRoma.
\v 22 Zvino chaunga chikavamukira pamwe, uye vatungamiriri vakavabvarurira nguvo dzavo vakaraira kuti va\add va\add*rove netsvimbo.
\v 23 Vakati vaisa mavanga mazhinji pamusoro pavo vaka\add va\add*kanda mutirongo, vakaraira murindi wetirongo kuti avachengete kwazvo;
\v 24 iye, agamuchira murairo wakadaro, wakavakanda mutirongo remukati, akasimbisa makumbo avo mudanda.
\v 25 Zvino panenge pakati peusiku Pauro naSirasi vakange vachinyengetera nekuimba nziyo kuna Mwari, uye vasungwa vaivanzwa;
\v 26 zvino pakarepo kwakavapo kudengenyeka kwenyika kukuru, zvekuti nheyo dzetirongo dzakazununguswa; pakarepo mikova yose ikazarurwa, nezvisungo zvevose zvikasunungurwa.
\v 27 Murindi wetirongo wakati apepuka, uye aona mikova yetirongo yakazarurwa, akavhomora munondo, oda kuzviuraya, achifunga kuti vasungwa vatiza.
\v 28 Asi Pauro wakadanidzira nenzwi guru, achiti: Usazvikuvadza; nekuti tiri muno tose.
\v 29 Zvino wakakumbira mwenje akasvetukiramo, ndokusvika achibvunda akawira pasi pamberi paPauro naSirasi,
\v 30 zvino akati avabudisira kunze akati: Madzishe, ndinofanira kuitei kuti ndiponeswe?
\v 31 Zvino vakati: Tenda kuna Ishe Jesu Kristu, zvino uchaponeswa iwe neimba yako.
\v 32 Zvino vakataura kwaari shoko raIshe, nekune vose vaiva mumba make.
\v 33 Ndokuvatora nenguva iyoyo yeusiku akasuka mavanga, ndokubhabhatidzwa pakarepo iye nevake vose.
\v 34 Zvino wakati avaisa mumba make ndokugadzika tafura pamberi \add pavo\add*, akafara nemhuri yake yose achitenda kuna Mwari.
\v 35 Zvino kwakati kwaedza vatungamiriri vakatuma mapurisa vachiti: Regai vanhu avo vaende.
\v 36 Murindi wetirongo ndokuudza Pauro mashoko iwayo, \add achiti\add*: Vatungamiriri vatuma \add shoko,\add* kuti musunungurwe; naizvozvo budai ikozvino muende murugare.
\v 37 Asi Pauro wakati kwavari: Vakatirova pachena tisina kubatwa mhosva \add tiri\add* vanhu vaRoma, vaka\add ti\add*kanda mutirongo, zvino ikozvino voda kutikanda panze chinyararire here? Haiwa, kwete! Asi ngavauye vamene vatibudise.
\v 38 Mapurisa ndokuudza vatungamiriri mashoko iwayo; zvino vakatya pavakanzwa kuti vaRoma,
\v 39 ndokuuya vakavakumbira, zvino vakavabudisa vakakumbira kuti vabude muguta.
\v 40 Zvino vakabuda mutirongo vakapinda kwaRidhia; ndokuti vaona hama, vakavanyaradza, ndokuenda.
